'''喬伊定律'''（'''Joy's Law'''）在[[天文學|天文學]]中是描述[[太陽黑子|太陽黑子]]傾斜的傾向。即前導黑子會比後隨黑子更靠近太陽的赤道，並且隨著緯度的增加，其傾斜越大<ref name=Hale1919>{{cite journal |title=The magnetic polarity of sun-spots |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_astrophysical-journal_1919-04_49_3/page/153 |vauthors=Hale GE, Ellerman F, Nicholson SB, Joy AH |journal=Astrophysical Journal |volume=49 |pages=153 |date=1919 |doi=10.1086/142452 |bibcode=1919ApJ....49..153H}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |title=Average properties of bipolar magnetic regions during sunspot cycle 21|author1=Wang, Y.-M. |author2=Sheeley, N. R., Jr. |journal=Solar Physics|volume=124 |pages=81–100|date=1989 |doi=10.1007/BF00146521|bibcode=1989SoPh..124...81W}}</ref><ref name=DSilva1992>{{cite journal |author=D'Silva S |title=Joy's Law and limits on the magnetic field strength at the bottom of the convection zone. |journal=The solar cycle; Proceedings of the National Solar Observatory/Sacramento Peak 12th Summer Workshop, ASP Conference Series (ASP: San Francisco) |volume=27 |pages=168 |date=1992 |id=1992ASPC...27..168D}}</ref><ref name=Tian2001>{{cite journal |title=Relationship in sign between tilt and twist in active region magnetic fields] |vauthors=Tian L, Bao S, Zhang H, Wang H |journal=Astronomy and Astrophysics |volume=374 |issue=1 |pages=294–300 |date=2001 |doi=10.1051/0004-6361:20010701|bibcode = 2001A&A...374..294T |doi-access=free }}</ref>。喬伊定律為[[太陽發電機|太陽發電機]]行動中的"阿爾法效應"提供了觀測上的支援<ref>{{Cite web|title = NASA/Marshall Solar Physics|url = http://solarscience.msfc.nasa.gov/dynamo.shtml|website = solarscience.msfc.nasa.gov|accessdate = 2015-12-10|archive-date = 2021-02-11|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210211022324/https://solarscience.msfc.nasa.gov/dynamo.shtml|dead-url = no}}</ref>。這個定律是以{{link-en|阿爾弗雷德·哈裡森·喬伊|Alfred Harrison Joy}}的名字命名。

